cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.DL 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify editor roles in student revision histories. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses topic modeling algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques, which are all relevant to the paper's methodology and analysis.
